  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nHere are fetching states for names and avatars.\r\nThe fetching state shows as a skeleton with a loading animation.\r\n\r\nIf fetching fails, we show a user the public key instead of the name and the fishbone illustration instead of the avatar.\r\n\r\n**Fetching:**\r\n<img width=\"910\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/109152754/205195867-681fbc24-b40c-455e-b772-289e5cd51bad.png\">\r\n<img width=\"909\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/109152754/205195910-b79f2da4-bbdb-489c-87e4-f56711b01d78.png\">\r\n<img width=\"637\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/109152754/205195954-d827de1c-2073-46f9-9b4a-a5748dc02edd.png\">\r\n\r\n**Fetching fails:**\r\n<img width=\"984\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/109152754/205196008-6362846e-ed7f-48c1-9c18-f44930b48c26.png\">\r\n<img width=\"982\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/109152754/205196047-70d28925-6fae-4b95-b49e-ccd51dd406a7.png\">\r\n<img width=\"684\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/109152754/205196093-01145e30-4df6-4bce-b27a-24a6e75a421a.png\">\r\n\r\nFigma link:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/Mr3rqxxgKJ2zMQ06UAKiWL/%F0%9F%92%AC-Chat%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=19715%3A494629&t=LK5jMgJwNinvUS4P-1\r\n\r\n\r\nThe loading state animation is linked with the wallet loading state here: https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/7661\r\n\r\nFeel free to ping me in Discord JuliaðŸŒˆ#1844 If anything is missing or if you would like to chat anything through  ðŸ™‚\r\n\r\n",
